                        <interp inst="t18470405-name-741" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN JUDGE.</persName>
                  </hi> I am an inspector of the Thames police. I received the prisoner in charge—I found 150lbs. of coals in the boat—they resembled those in the barge—he had this little tin pan with him, which would enable him to take the coals out.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> They were coals that were of no use; I bought them to support my family.</p>
